---
title: Cheesy Chicken Enchiladas with Pickled Onion & Cos Salad
description: These easy chicken enchiladas get their signature cheesy topping from some time under the grill, making them a faster and simpler way to enjoy the classic Mexican flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c3e7e8bc445fa29f207f802-692a6874.jpg
